My Morning Checklist (Work)
===========================

Prepare
-------

[ ] Fetch water and coffee

Sweep
-----

[ ] Check work calendar, anything pressing?
[ ] Process work email inbox (remember 2-minute rule)
[ ] Close email app

Process
-------

[ ] Process OmniFocus inbox (top to bottom) (remember 2-minute rule)
[ ] Review all projects in Review tab
[ ] Process Slack notifications

Start
-----

